{"tid":1933221,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇物理學高人解答下呢個問題","createTime":"2020-03-19T07:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T12:56:03.000Z","uid":34339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a3821440c8d6f0548792abb9fc2b85af1e393f89","tid":1933221,"uid":34339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"我當時沿住大路直行，突然有部貨櫃車從小路右轉cut出黎大路，勾住我部車扯住我行，仲要屈我從後撞佢，請問各巴絲打有冇方法證明我係被撞嘅一個<br />\n<br />\n案發現場情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NeE9tB9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNeE9tB9.jpg&h=a2e38ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司機位倒後鏡被扯到往前反<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANhSrpJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANhSrpJ.jpg&h=bb23d6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDr0Ah3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDr0Ah3.jpg&h=210fc4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對方貨櫃車油缸頭有撞凹位同埋由前往後嘅扯痕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6Pac5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6Pac5s.jpg&h=fc63b968&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VhOKb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VhOKb8.jpg&h=faad9ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油缸尾部完好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhnvc6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdhnvc6f.jpg&h=32b43568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n護欄破爛地方喺前方<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DVGTaSG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDVGTaSG.jpg&h=7efa0d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n右邊車頭泵把被扯爛，沙板出現一個大插孔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4Hi6rM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4Hi6rM.jpg&h=25003132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n右邊後窗被壓爆，但司機車窗完好<br />\n右邊前後車門頂被壓，出現一個前圓後尖嘅壓痕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkphCy4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkphCy4.jpg&h=670b612c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54ONZOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54ONZOi.jpg&h=1b7b6217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n右後門被壓痕明顯睇到方向係由後向前<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZs7fm3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZs7fm3.jpg&h=a7698ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各巴絲打提出意見證明係我比貨櫃車扯住黎行"},{"pid":"4fab9439f96b66acf83aee37181aed5e6310f1bf","tid":1933221,"uid":46911,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"唔洗物理學高手<br />\n你有車cam就得"},{"pid":"96d0bce3be3355c48c9fd4e31ca9ad1f494983e0","tid":1933221,"uid":308251,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:26:51.000Z","msg":"繼續吹，點睇都係貨車佬入緊大路，你條柒頭分心撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aea6f4fb4f2aa7b930bf2968955ffc04ecd2526","tid":1933221,"uid":34339,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"4fab9439f96b66acf83aee37181aed5e6310f1bf","tid":1933221,"uid":46911,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"唔洗物理學高手<br />\n你有車cam就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:38:57.000Z","msg":"車cam咁啱神左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c02a66c409118661a2a7052a88af8065f61ce9c","tid":1933221,"uid":34339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"96d0bce3be3355c48c9fd4e31ca9ad1f494983e0","tid":1933221,"uid":308251,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:26:51.000Z","msg":"繼續吹，點睇都係貨車佬入緊大路，你條柒頭分心撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"氣袋冇爆<br />\n啲嘢又係勾出黎<br />\n點樣我撞佢"},{"pid":"8f443c79f71c906c36cbc2735e16950cf21c9a8b","tid":1933221,"uid":245590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07